text: Patricia Kalember (born December 30, 1957) is an American television and movie actress. She is best known for playing in the TV drama Sisters. Many sources list Kalember's birth date as December 30, 1956 instead of 1957. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from New York (state) Category:1957 births Category:Living people
